1. Register app - https://github.com/settings/developers
2. Get the Client ID and Client Secret
3. Visit the following url to get Github Code - https://github.com/login/oauth/authorize?client_id=<CLIENTID>&scope=<USERNAME>:<EMAIL>,repo
4. Get the Github Code
5. visit the following url and Get the Access Token - https://github.com/login/oauth/access_token?client_id=<CLIENTID>&client_secret=<CLIENTSECRET>&code=<CODE>
6. copy the access token
7. done
